Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.7 43/53] scsi: mptscsih: Fix read sense data size
Date:   Wed,  1 Jul 2020 21:21:52 -0400
Message-Id: <20200702012202.2700645-43-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
